
Where to apply:
	1. class
		- inner class 
	2. variable
		- static
		- instance 
		- local 
	3. method
		- static
		- instance
	4. interface
		- public
	5. enum
		

- public 
  - anywhere
   
- private 
  - within class/abstract class
  - not private in interface

- <java default behaviour>
  - package level access

- protected
  - within package
  - diff package - can access by using child class object only
